### Configuracoes Iniciais (Variaveis)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 0. Login para obter token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "contato@opticaflow.com.br",
  "senha": "11222333000181"
}

###

@token = COLE_SEU_TOKEN
@empresaId = COLE_ID_EMPRESA
@convenioId = COLE_ID_CONVENIO

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------
### CONVENIO
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Criar convenio
POST {{baseUrl}}/convenio
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "nome": "Convenio Visao Saude",
  "registro": "REG-12345",
  "ativo": true
}

### 2. Listar convenios por empresa
GET {{baseUrl}}/convenio/empresa/{{empresaId}}?page=1&limit=10&search=visao&ativo=true
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Buscar convenio por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/convenio/{{convenioId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Atualizar convenio
PUT {{baseUrl}}/convenio/{{convenioId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nome": "Convenio Visao Saude Plus",
  "registro": "REG-98765",
  "ativo": true
}

### 5. Teste negativo: nome duplicado na mesma empresa
POST {{baseUrl}}/convenio
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "nome": "Convenio Visao Saude Plus"
}

### 6. Deletar convenio (somente sem clientes/atendimentos vinculados)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/convenio/{{convenioId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}